{"tid":605893,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"陳根記殺入大埔","createTime":"2018-03-26T05:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T03:17:17.000Z","uid":18391,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"20fd107b246d92fcef8c8a380e9996706a1191e2","tid":605893,"uid":18391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"陳根記殺入大埔開店！<br />\n<br />\n老闆周生話，大埔店預計 5 月開張。新店增設午市，有上海、四川麵食，晚市可以食返招牌嘅 Wasabi 蟹籽手撕雞等小菜！至於禾輋嘅大牌檔，已續約至今年年底。Fans 繼續有好嘢食！<br />\n<br />\n【Info 】<br />\n陳根記（大埔店）<br />\n地址：大埔大明里儲金閣C和D座地下12-14號舖<br />\n預計 5 月開業<br />\nSource: May Tam Snow<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該係東江雞果個位，到時連埋陳漢記d人流實塞爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec3bda0f7f58fe60cdc47d2bea99f1d877a9f43","tid":605893,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":29,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62eb9884bb5a8118ff2438e261bb8f7b5e1e1bc2","tid":605893,"uid":77556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5ec3bda0f7f58fe60cdc47d2bea99f1d877a9f43","tid":605893,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":29,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"有冇咁快。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c3166a56d6317ca85be6b35e2a75a91570a142fc","tid":605893,"uid":60588,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:17:38.000Z","msg":"陳根記比人瘋狂吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a68841cfbd336470c6e92d7f0e2859404cdad10","tid":605893,"uid":18391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec3bda0f7f58fe60cdc47d2bea99f1d877a9f43","tid":605893,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":29,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"執左啦"},{"pid":"2bf4502e3cdda7ae43d7302976de109bd81ce15f","tid":605893,"uid":9269,"like"